longBusinessSummary: Global Indemnity Group, LLC, through its subsidiaries, provides specialty property and casualty insurance, and reinsurance products worldwide. It operates in two segments, Commercial Specialty and Reinsurance Operations. The Commercial Specialty segment distributes property and casualty insurance products; and general liability products for small commercial businesses through a network of wholesale general agents. The Reinsurance Operations segment provides third-party treaty reinsurance for casualty insurance and reinsurance companies, as well as professional liability products to companies through brokers. The company was founded in 2003 and is based in Wilmington, Delaware.
